QArpWatch
Simple GUI that check if your gateway mac adresse change, usefull to detected MITM by arp poisoning.
Actually you need to be on clean network before run the software, it can't detect if the network look suspicious maybe in a future version.

A last win32 build is availble here:
https://github.com/downloads/y0ug/QArpWatch/QArpWatch.zip

To build it
$ qmake
$ make
$ ./QArpWatch


Ubuntu dep to build it
$ sudo apt-get install qt4-dev-tools
